<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>ABIDE WITH ME !</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Ka kawm ah um in, nitak ahi tai,
 Khuo a thim, Lalpa, Ka kawmah um in;
 Panpih lungmuon ding beia ka um tieng,
 Panpih bei, Panpihpa, ei umpih in.

[V2]
 2. Hin khuo kallo a mangthai ding ahi,
 Lei kipahna, lopina a bei hi;
 Ka muh theih cheng, danglam in a sie zel,
 Danglam thei lo, Nang in ei umpih in.

[V3]
 3. Lengte Leng bangin lauhum in hung ki'n,
 Zainem leh pha'n hihdamna tawh hungin
 Mitthi thiek hulin, lunggil hihhalh in,
 Mi gilo Guolpa, Nang ei umpih in.

[V4]
 4. Hun chengin nei umpihna ka ngai hi,
 Na lungsietna maiin thepna a zo;
 Nang bang ei pui leh muon ding kuo a um?
 Vannim leh ni vakah ei umpih in.

[V5]
 5. Nang nei panpih leh dogal ka lau puoi,
 Natna a khawk puoi, kah le a khawk puoi;
 Thihna, na gu, than na zawhna khawia?
 Guolzo zel ing ka, Nang nei umpih chun.

[V6]
 6. Ka mit ka sin tieng ka kawmah umin,
 Lungkham salhvak in, Van lam ei hilh in;
 Van zingkhuo a vak, leh lim a beimang,
 Damsung, thih hun in le ei umpih in.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>175</hymn_number>
</song>